Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.activity.Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicOperatorBorderControlActivity, BasicPassengerBorderControlActivity, CheckpointActivity, ETDCheckActivity, ExitActivity, FacilityActivity, GateActivity, LuggageCheckActivity, LuggageDropActivity, OperatorBorderControlActivity, OperatorCheckInActivity, PassengerBorderControlActivity, PassengerCheckInActivity, PhysicalCheckActivity, QueueActivity, TravelDocumentCheckActivity, XRayActivity

    public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
implements Updatable
    An activity is something that an agent can do. An activity will be updated every simulation step and internally updates its state based on its environment.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
